OL,3,CITV News' Rageh Omaar thanks viewers
OL,4,Cfor good wishes
OL,6,FITV News presenter Rageh Omaar is
OL,7,F"recovering at home with his family"
OL,8,Fafter being treated in hospital and
OL,9,Fhas thanked everyone for their
OL,10,F"kindness and good wishes".
OL,12,FOn Saturday, an ITV News spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We appreciate viewers of last
OL,14,Fnight's News At Ten were concerned
OL,15,Fabout Rageh Omaar's wellbeing.
OL,17,F"Following medical treatment at
OL,18,Fhospital, he is now recovering at home
OL,19,Fwith his family.
