OL,3,CITV News' Rageh Omaar thanks viewers
OL,4,Cfor good wishes
OL,6,F"We are wishing Rageh a speedy
OL,7,Frecovery and look forward to him being
OL,8,Fback on screen when he feels ready."
OL,10,FIn a statement shared by ITV News,
OL,11,FRageh Omaar added: "I would like to
OL,12,Fthank everyone for their kindness and
OL,13,Fgood wishes, especially all the
OL,14,Fmedical staff, all my wonderful
OL,15,Fcolleagues at ITV News, and our
OL,16,Fviewers who expressed concern.
OL,18,F"At the time, I was determined to
OL,19,Ffinish presenting the programme. I am
OL,20,Fgrateful for all the support I've been
OL,21,Fgiven."
